data.description: Step into the perfect blend of comfort and beauty in this beautiful Hidden Springs home. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by new Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring that spans the entire first floor, lending a fresh and modern ambiance to the space. With ample room for both formal dinners and casual game nights, this home provides the ideal setting for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the great room, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. From there, step out onto the expansive deck and down to the beautifully landscaped backyard, where relaxation awaits amidst the tranquility of nature. As you reach to the second floor, you'll discover a versatile loft space, ideal for a home office or study area. Two secondary bedrooms and a shared bath, offer comfortable accommodations for family members or guests. Tucked away down the hall is your personal sanctuary – the primary bedroom featuring an ensuite bathroom, providing a serene retreat at the end of each day.    Enhancing the allure of this home is its exceptional location! Just a stone's throw away from King Springs Elementary, convenience and accessibility are at your fingertips. When you're craving a night out, head over to The Battery to catch a Braves game or indulge in a culinary adventure at one of the numerous restaurants while thre. With its proximity to major transportation arteries like 285 and Atlanta Hartsfield Airport, as well as the vibrant energy of Midtown, this home offers unparalleled convenience and connectivity to everything Atlanta has to offer. Whether you're seeking entertainment, dining, or easy access to travel hubs, this prime location ensures that all your lifestyle needs are effortlessly met.
